findings.remediation:
Add to hash.json (or equivalent config):
  "monitoring": {
    "enabled": true,
    "db_path": "workspace/memory/.activity.db",
    "retention_days": 30
  }

Enable monitoring with retention in hash.json:
  "monitoring": {
    "enabled": true,
    "retention_days": 30,
    "prompt_audit": true
  }
